					<tr>
						<td style="height: 30px;">&nbsp;</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td align="left" style="padding: 0 45px;">
						<p>Dear&nbsp;{{{Recipient.FirstName}}},</p>

						<p>Could you please complete the short appraisal below regarding [Nurse’s Name], who is currently on contract with your facility? If you would prefer, I’d be more than happy to arrange a quick&nbsp;phone call instead. Just let me know a convenient day and time.<br />
						<br />
						<strong>Facility Support / Nurse Appraisal</strong></p>

						<ul>
							<li>NUM / Line Manager:</li>
							<li>Contract Dates:</li>
						</ul>

						<p><strong>Questions:</strong></p>

						<ol>
							<li>Are you happy with our nurse on contract at present?</li>
							<li>Are there any issues with their practice or performance that we should be aware of?</li>
							<li>Are they working well with other staff?</li>
						</ol>

						<p>Please note: if you would like to extend the contract, we would be happy to facilitate this,just liaise with your LHD Recruitment Team to coordinate.<br />
						<br />
						If there are any performance issues, incidents, or concerns, please let us know. We’re here to support you and will gladly work with you to resolve any matters.<br />
						<br />
						Thank you in advance for your feedback. I look forward to receiving your appraisal.<br />
						&nbsp;<br />
						Kind regards,<br />
						{{{Sender.FirstName}}}&nbsp;{{{Sender.LastName}}}<br />
						Alliance Rural &amp; Remote Health</p>
						</td>
					</tr>
